data.title: FAITH Global
data.meta_description:
FAITH Global | 589 followers on LinkedIn. Faith Global is a non-profit membership based community of like-minded professionals and organizations. It's brands support faith in thought, faith in people, faith in free speech, faith in health, faith in education, faith in religion and faith in entertainment.

It is the fundamental belief of Faith Global that regardless of religious or spiritual affiliation we can all work together in international cooperation through our faith in each other.
